Description: A lightweight package aims to provide an easy-to-use interface for estimating marginal or unconditional Hazard Ratio (HR) and 
  Restricted Mean Survival Time (RMST) when adjusting prognostic covariates in clinical trials.
Maintainer: Xinlei Deng <xinlei.deng@novartis.com>
